	<h1 class="title">吴秀波的这部民国剧虽然没红，但是真的挺好看</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-30 07:21:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19917/medium/19917.jpg?1451379671" alt="" />			
	</div>
